189
00:18:52,714 --> 00:18:54,799
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- How's it going, bud?
- Oh, you know.</font>

190
00:18:54,883 --> 00:18:57,969
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Just a quiet night at home,
settling in with a good book.</font>

191
00:18:58,053 --> 00:19:00,930
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- And you? What's up with you?
- I was just calling to say we're here.</font>

192
00:19:01,014 --> 00:19:03,433
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But now every word out of your mouth
ls making me suspicious.</font>

193
00:19:03,516 --> 00:19:04,558
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font>

194
00:19:04,643 --> 00:19:08,772
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You got to relax, buddy.
You're at the Four Seasons Oahu.</font>

195
00:19:08,855 --> 00:19:11,274
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Have a mai tai.
Enjoy some time with your wife.</font>

196
00:19:11,358 --> 00:19:13,193
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Get sunburned somewhere embarrassing.</font>

197
00:19:13,276 --> 00:19:15,695
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This weekend is about you.</font>

198
00:19:15,779 --> 00:19:18,364
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You know what? You're right.
We power-bumped on it.</font>

199
00:19:18,448 --> 00:19:19,866
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So whatever it is you're doing,</font>

200
00:19:19,949 --> 00:19:22,451
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sure you can undo it
by the time we get home, yeah?</font>

201
00:19:22,535 --> 00:19:27,035
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Exactly! I mean, I am deeply offended
by such accusations!</font>

202
00:19:27,248 --> 00:19:28,958
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So, how's Rachel's fiancée?</font>

203
00:19:29,042 --> 00:19:32,128
<font face="Comic Sans MS">ls he as good-looking in person
as he is in pictures?</font>

204
00:19:34,130 --> 00:19:35,589
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Somehow better-looking.</font>

205
00:19:35,674 --> 00:19:38,551
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wow! You're about to be
the third best-looking dude in the family.</font>

206
00:19:38,635 --> 00:19:40,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But, hey, still on the podium.</font>

207
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:44,098
<font face="Comic Sans MS">All right,
I better go and introduce myself.</font>

208
00:19:44,808 --> 00:19:46,142
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Stay out of trouble.</font>

209
00:19:46,226 --> 00:19:50,688
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Trouble? Don't worry.
Everything here is completely normal.</font>

210
00:19:50,772 --> 00:19:52,231
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Uh-huh. Night, bud.</font>

211
00:19:53,233 --> 00:19:55,109
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey! I was just coming over to say hi.</font>

212
00:19:55,193 --> 00:19:57,945
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You've got a lot of nerve coming up
in here after what you did to my fiancée.</font>

213
00:19:59,364 --> 00:20:01,074
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Wait. What?
- Totaling her car?</font>

214
00:20:01,741 --> 00:20:04,326
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Leaving her tied to a chair?
I should rip you limb from limb.</font>

215
00:20:08,456 --> 00:20:10,249
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, my God, look at your face!</font>

216
00:20:10,333 --> 00:20:12,251
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Tommy, breathe, baby. Breathe.
I was kidding.</font>

217
00:20:12,335 --> 00:20:14,253
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hey, man, I was totally kidding.
- Okay.</font>

218
00:20:16,131 --> 00:20:17,841
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- You were kidding.
- Yeah.</font>

219
00:20:17,924 --> 00:20:20,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry. Rachel put me up to it.
It was totally her idea.</font>

220
00:20:21,302 --> 00:20:22,636
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That rascal.</font>

221
00:20:22,721 --> 00:20:26,850
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Listen, I don't know if you're aware.
Rachel does not care for you at all.</font>

222
00:20:27,684 --> 00:20:28,935
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm aware. Yeah.</font>

223
00:20:29,561 --> 00:20:31,688
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Seriously, bro, you got work to do.</font>

224
00:20:31,771 --> 00:20:33,230
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hey!
- Hey.</font>

225
00:20:33,314 --> 00:20:35,607
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Good to see you! Thanks for coming, Tom.</font>

226
00:20:35,692 --> 00:20:37,735
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Really glad you came.
- Really?</font>

227
00:20:39,696 --> 00:20:41,739
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Great to see you, too. Congratulations.</font>

228
00:20:41,823 --> 00:20:44,283
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I mean, you guys seem
really happy together.</font>

229
00:20:44,367 --> 00:20:45,951
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You know, you're all right,
Thomas Wachowski.</font>

230
00:20:47,912 --> 00:20:50,247
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Can we bury the hatchet?
- I'd love that.</font>

231
00:20:50,331 --> 00:20:51,832
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Yeah?
- Yeah.</font>

232
00:20:51,916 --> 00:20:54,376
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- All right, bring it in!
- All right! Great.</font>

233
00:20:55,170 --> 00:20:57,755
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And if you screw up my wedding,
I will end you.</font>

234
00:21:01,843 --> 00:21:04,720
<font face="Comic Sans MS">All right, Ozzy,
it's movie night at Casa de Sonic,</font>

235
00:21:04,804 --> 00:21:06,055
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and it's your turn to pick.</font>

236
00:21:06,139 --> 00:21:08,683
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But I am not watching Snow Dogs again.</font>

237
00:21:08,767 --> 00:21:11,436
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That movie is the worst!</font>

238
00:21:14,439 --> 00:21:15,648
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Blackout!</font>

239
00:21:17,275 --> 00:21:19,193
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Ozzy.</font>

240
00:21:19,903 --> 00:21:21,446
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sorry, buddy. Everything's okay.</font>

241
00:21:28,703 --> 00:21:31,622
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Excuse me. We did not order a poltergeist.</font>

242
00:21:41,925 --> 00:21:45,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS">If this is the pizza guy,
this is really unprofessional.</font>

243
00:22:03,321 --> 00:22:04,613
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Eggman?</font>

244
00:22:08,117 --> 00:22:11,036
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hello, hedgehog.</font>

245
00:22:12,330 --> 00:22:13,622
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Did you miss me?</font>

246
00:22:14,999 --> 00:22:19,336
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't know how you got back,
but you made a big mistake coming here.</font>

247
00:22:19,420 --> 00:22:22,256
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Au conftraire, mon frere.</font>

248
00:22:22,841 --> 00:22:25,301
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The mistake was thinking you'd won.</font>

249
00:22:25,385 --> 00:22:27,845
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But that was just a prelude,
an hors d'oeuvre,</font>

250
00:22:27,929 --> 00:22:30,097
<font face="Comic Sans MS">an aperitif, an amuse-bouche.</font>

251
00:22:30,181 --> 00:22:31,473
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I get it.</font>

252
00:22:33,101 --> 00:22:34,602
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I don't think you do.</font>

253
00:22:34,686 --> 00:22:36,604
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But you're about to.</font>

254
00:22:36,688 --> 00:22:39,232
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And so will that idiot sheriff
and his wife.</font>

255
00:22:41,818 --> 00:22:43,361
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And your little dog too!</font>

256
00:23:02,547 --> 00:23:03,714
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Pitiful.</font>

257
00:23:03,798 --> 00:23:06,425
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What? Who are you?</font>

258
00:23:07,886 --> 00:23:10,597
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Where are my manners?</font>

259
00:23:11,306 --> 00:23:14,684
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sonic, meet Knuckles.</font>

260
00:23:14,767 --> 00:23:16,977
<font face="Comic Sans MS">My new BFFAE.</font>

261
00:23:17,061 --> 00:23:20,439
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Bestest friend forever and ever!</font>

262
00:23:20,523 --> 00:23:23,651
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Look, Robotnik, I don't care
who you brought to help you.</font>

263
00:23:23,735 --> 00:23:25,570
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You're never going to get my power.</font>

264
00:23:25,653 --> 00:23:28,238
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Do I look like I need your power?</font>

265
00:23:38,791 --> 00:23:43,003
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So nice when diabolical evil
lives up to the hype.</font>

266
00:23:46,007 --> 00:23:47,341
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Where is it?</font>

267
00:23:47,425 --> 00:23:50,469
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You want it? Here it comes.</font>

268
00:23:50,553 --> 00:23:55,053
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I was expecting more of you.
You're unskilled.</font>

269
00:23:56,059 --> 00:23:57,310
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Untrained.</font>

270
00:23:58,853 --> 00:24:01,188
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And unworthy!</font>

271
00:24:02,649 --> 00:24:06,194
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You forgot one. Unstoppable.</font>

272
00:24:32,136 --> 00:24:35,973
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It is my destiny
to do what my ancestors could not--</font>

273
00:24:36,057 --> 00:24:40,227
<font face="Comic Sans MS">To restore the ultimate power
to the home of my people.</font>

274
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:44,773
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Ultimate power?
I don't know what you're talking about.</font>

275
00:24:44,857 --> 00:24:46,066
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You've got the wrong guy.</font>

276
00:24:46,150 --> 00:24:48,318
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Ultimate power?</font>

277
00:24:48,820 --> 00:24:51,614
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now you're speaking my language.</font>

278
00:24:51,698 --> 00:24:54,867
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't play dumb with me,
apprentice of Longclaw.</font>

279
00:24:54,951 --> 00:24:56,410
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You knew Longclaw?</font>

280
00:24:56,494 --> 00:25:00,623
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Longclaw and her people were
the sworn enemy of my tribe, the Echidna.</font>

281
00:25:00,707 --> 00:25:05,207
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We fought and died at their hands,
and now you will die at mine.</font>

282
00:25:16,389 --> 00:25:18,557
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on. Get in! I'm on your side.</font>

283
00:25:18,641 --> 00:25:20,559
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry. Who are you?</font>

284
00:25:21,811 --> 00:25:23,521
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You know what? It doesn't matter.</font>

285
00:25:26,065 --> 00:25:28,108
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Get us out of here! Go, go, go!</font>

286
00:25:32,321 --> 00:25:33,322
<font face="Comic Sans MS">He's gone rabid!</font>

287
00:25:35,575 --> 00:25:36,993
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Gross! Is he licking it?</font>

288
00:25:38,202 --> 00:25:39,494
<font face="Comic Sans MS">See ya!</font>

289
00:25:39,579 --> 00:25:41,872
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Make sure to get your shots, Eggman!</font>

290
00:25:55,762 --> 00:25:59,432
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wow. Okay. Let me just say
it is an honor to finally meet you, Sonic.</font>

291
00:25:59,515 --> 00:26:01,058
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Is it okay if I call you Sonic?</font>

292
00:26:01,142 --> 00:26:03,894
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Everyone calls me Tails.
You're probably wondering why.</font>

293
00:26:03,978 --> 00:26:06,355
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me guess. Because of the extra tail?</font>

294
00:26:06,439 --> 00:26:08,357
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's right!
I should've known you'd get that.</font>

295
00:26:08,441 --> 00:26:12,153
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Cool. Also, what is going on?
Robotnik's back?</font>

296
00:26:12,236 --> 00:26:14,696
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And who is
Clifford the Big Red Rage Monster?</font>

297
00:26:15,364 --> 00:26:17,324
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's Knuckles, the last of the Echidnas</font>

298
00:26:17,408 --> 00:26:19,827
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and the most dangerous warrior
in the galaxy.</font>

299
00:26:19,911 --> 00:26:21,996
<font face="Comic Sans MS">He's obsessed with finding
the Master Emerald.</font>

300
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:24,415
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you serious? The Master Emerald?</font>

301
00:26:24,499 --> 00:26:26,125
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's just a bedtime story.</font>

302
00:26:26,209 --> 00:26:27,627
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, he believes it's real.</font>

303
00:26:27,710 --> 00:26:30,003
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And he must think
you're the key to finding it.</font>

304
00:26:32,215 --> 00:26:34,050
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Red light! Give me the wheel!</font>

305
00:26:34,133 --> 00:26:35,968
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Hey, what are you--
- Move your foot.</font>

306
00:26:43,726 --> 00:26:45,018
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I think we lost him.</font>

307
00:26:52,944 --> 00:26:55,529
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We did not lose him.
We definitely did not lose him!</font>

308
00:27:00,785 --> 00:27:02,953
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I've got an idea. Do you trust me?</font>

309
00:27:03,037 --> 00:27:05,247
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Of course not! I literally just met you!</font>

310
00:27:05,331 --> 00:27:07,416
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Just let me-- Come on!
- What are you doing?</font>

311
00:27:26,394 --> 00:27:27,645
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We're flying.</font>

312
00:27:28,354 --> 00:27:30,439
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Did your butt just turn into a helicopter?</font>

313
00:27:31,816 --> 00:27:33,442
<font face="Comic Sans MS">A butt-copter!</font>

314
00:27:34,026 --> 00:27:37,362
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Only Sonic the Hedgehog
could come up with something like that.</font>

315
00:27:52,461 --> 00:27:54,629
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Foxy move.</font>

316
00:27:55,882 --> 00:27:57,925
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You want something done right...</font>

317
00:27:59,218 --> 00:28:02,221
<font face="Comic Sans MS">you have to hire someone
you can push around.</font>

318
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:05,265
<font face="Comic Sans MS">All caps.</font>

319
00:28:23,618 --> 00:28:24,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Doctor,</font>

320
00:28:25,828 --> 00:28:26,954
<font face="Comic Sans MS">where are you?</font>

321
00:28:33,753 --> 00:28:34,795
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Freak.</font>

322
00:28:43,054 --> 00:28:45,347
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry, folks.</font>

323
00:28:45,431 --> 00:28:47,808
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I have to close early. Everybody out!</font>

324
00:28:47,892 --> 00:28:50,978
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Everybody out.
Thank you for visiting the Mean Bean.</font>

325
00:28:51,062 --> 00:28:53,105
<font face="Comic Sans MS">All right, good night. Good night.</font>

326
00:29:12,291 --> 00:29:13,333
<font face="Comic Sans MS">He's back.</font>

327
00:29:15,044 --> 00:29:17,046
<font face="Comic Sans MS">He's back!</font>

328
00:30:11,809 --> 00:30:14,019
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's more like it.</font>

329
00:30:15,021 --> 00:30:17,857
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I've been re-hatched!</font>

330
00:30:29,410 --> 00:30:33,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So, my massively metacarpaled friend,</font>

331
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:35,374
<font face="Comic Sans MS">you mentioned...</font>

332
00:30:37,251 --> 00:30:39,253
<font face="Comic Sans MS">ultimate power.</font>

333
00:30:39,337 --> 00:30:40,338
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Back at the house?</font>

334
00:30:40,421 --> 00:30:42,047
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The Master Emerald?</font>

335
00:30:42,131 --> 00:30:43,507
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It does not concern you.</font>

336
00:30:43,591 --> 00:30:46,594
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I got you off that planet
and you brought me to the hedgehog.</font>

337
00:30:46,677 --> 00:30:48,762
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We have no more use for each other.</font>

338
00:30:48,846 --> 00:30:51,181
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Well, I hate to be a contrarian, but...</font>

339
00:30:52,099 --> 00:30:53,225
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I think we might.</font>

340
00:30:54,727 --> 00:30:57,187
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You think these machines
are a match for me?</font>

341
00:30:57,271 --> 00:31:00,732
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I will shatter them
like the bones from a fallen--</font>

342
00:31:01,609 --> 00:31:02,735
<font face="Comic Sans MS">They are stairs.</font>

343
00:31:08,449 --> 00:31:12,619
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You see, Earth is my turf, G.</font>

344
00:31:13,120 --> 00:31:15,872
<font face="Comic Sans MS">If you don't know how to floss,
you'll be lost without me.</font>

345
00:31:15,956 --> 00:31:18,500
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I understand nothing
of what you just said.</font>

346
00:31:18,584 --> 00:31:22,963
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I help you retrieve the Emerald,
and you use it to...</font>

347
00:31:24,256 --> 00:31:28,756
<font face="Comic Sans MS">destroy the hedgehog!</font>

348
00:31:29,970 --> 00:31:31,680
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You're suggesting an alliance.</font>

349
00:31:31,764 --> 00:31:35,893
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Around here we simply
grip each other's hands tightly.</font>

350
00:31:41,273 --> 00:31:44,901
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You truculent space bumpkin!</font>

351
00:31:44,985 --> 00:31:47,153
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You've crushed my favorite hand!</font>

352
00:31:47,822 --> 00:31:49,740
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Really? My hand is uninjured.</font>

353
00:31:50,950 --> 00:31:53,202
<font face="Comic Sans MS">But I'm now convinced of your commitment.</font>

354
00:31:53,285 --> 00:31:55,203
<font face="Comic Sans MS">"Oh, goody,"</font>

355
00:31:55,287 --> 00:31:58,790
<font face="Comic Sans MS">he exclaimed,
while he reset two of his knuckles.</font>

356
00:31:58,874 --> 00:32:01,209
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm...</font>

357
00:32:01,293 --> 00:32:05,793
<font face="Comic Sans MS">delighted to be on the same team.</font>

358
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:15,432
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Road trip!</font>

359
00:32:16,016 --> 00:32:18,059
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'll let you stick your nose
out the window.</font>

360
00:32:20,271 --> 00:32:22,022
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sonic, where are we?</font>

361
00:32:22,106 --> 00:32:24,483
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Welcome to the Wade Cave.</font>

362
00:32:24,567 --> 00:32:27,611
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Which is something
I hope to someday say to a woman.</font>

363
00:32:27,695 --> 00:32:29,363
<font face="Comic Sans MS">A woman who's not my mom.</font>

364
00:32:29,447 --> 00:32:31,407
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wade, focus.</font>

365
00:32:31,490 --> 00:32:35,202
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We need to figure out why Knuckles thinks
I'm the key to finding the Master Emerald.</font>

366
00:32:35,286 --> 00:32:37,204
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And why did he mention Longclaw?</font>

367
00:32:37,788 --> 00:32:40,040
<font face="Comic Sans MS">There must be a connection.</font>

368
00:32:40,624 --> 00:32:42,042
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wait a minute. There is.</font>

369
00:32:42,585 --> 00:32:46,505
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Look. There's an emerald symbol
on the map Longclaw gave me.</font>

370
00:32:46,589 --> 00:32:48,465
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I never knew what it meant before.</font>

371
00:32:49,175 --> 00:32:50,843
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Something's happening.</font>

372
00:33:03,981 --> 00:33:05,357
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Longclaw?</font>

373
00:33:05,441 --> 00:33:06,984
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hello, Sonic.</font>

374
00:33:07,067 --> 00:33:10,445
<font face="Comic Sans MS">If you're watching this,
then something has happened to me.</font>

375
00:33:10,529 --> 00:33:13,365
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And I pray
you've made it to Earth unharmed.</font>

376
00:33:13,866 --> 00:33:18,161
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This world has been chosen
for a very important reason.</font>

377
00:33:18,245 --> 00:33:21,873
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's the secret location
of the Master Emerald.</font>

378
00:33:24,001 --> 00:33:27,629
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The Emerald has the power
to turn thoughts into reality.</font>

379
00:33:28,130 --> 00:33:30,632
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Like the Stay Puft Marshmallow Man
from Ghostbusters.</font>

380
00:33:31,383 --> 00:33:35,470
<font face="Comic Sans MS">In the wrong hands it could threaten
all life in the universe.</font>

381
00:33:35,554 --> 00:33:38,473
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Protecting the Emerald was my sacred duty.</font>

382
00:33:38,557 --> 00:33:42,227
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And now I must pass
that responsibility to you.</font>

383
00:33:43,354 --> 00:33:46,023
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This is my moment.</font>

384
00:33:46,106 --> 00:33:49,567
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Follow the map, find the Emerald,
and keep it safe.</font>

385
00:33:50,194 --> 00:33:51,737
<font face="Comic Sans MS">My dear Sonic,</font>

386
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:54,781
<font face="Comic Sans MS">you have a heart
like no creature I've ever known.</font>

387
00:33:55,407 --> 00:33:57,075
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I love you so much.</font>

388
00:33:58,744 --> 00:33:59,953
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Goodbye.</font>

389
00:34:01,330 --> 00:34:03,123
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No, no, wait.</font>

390
00:34:10,256 --> 00:34:12,132
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I won't let you down, Longclaw.</font>

391
00:34:14,093 --> 00:34:17,221
<font face="Comic Sans MS">So is that your dad?</font>

392
00:34:17,304 --> 00:34:18,763
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font>

393
00:34:18,847 --> 00:34:19,722
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No?</font>

394
00:34:20,599 --> 00:34:23,435
<font face="Comic Sans MS">According to this map,
the first clue is in Siberia.</font>

395
00:34:23,519 --> 00:34:25,812
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a compass
that will lead to the Emerald.</font>

396
00:34:25,896 --> 00:34:28,815
<font face="Comic Sans MS">And with Knuckles already here,
it's a race.</font>

397
00:34:28,899 --> 00:34:29,900
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Knuckles?</font>

398
00:34:30,651 --> 00:34:32,444
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I knew a kid in middle school
named Knuckles.</font>

399
00:34:32,528 --> 00:34:34,363
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Could fit his whole fist in his mouth.</font>

400
00:34:34,446 --> 00:34:38,575
<font face="Comic Sans MS">If this is the same Knuckles,
we are screwed.</font>

401
00:34:38,659 --> 00:34:41,078
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This Knuckles, that Knuckles.
It doesn't matter.</font>

402
00:34:41,161 --> 00:34:42,829
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We're gonna get there first.</font>

403
00:34:45,833 --> 00:34:47,584
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What do you mean, "we"?</font>

404
00:34:47,668 --> 00:34:48,960
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You're coming with me.</font>

405
00:34:49,044 --> 00:34:50,378
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No, no, no.</font>

406
00:34:50,462 --> 00:34:53,673
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I just came here to warn you.
I'm not a field guy.</font>

407
00:34:53,757 --> 00:34:57,552
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't worry. I got your back.
I won't let anything happen to you.</font>

408
00:34:59,013 --> 00:35:02,766
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a power bump.
On Earth, it means an unbreakable promise.</font>

409
00:35:02,850 --> 00:35:05,561
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay, I'm in.</font>

410
00:35:21,285 --> 00:35:23,662
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Doctor. It's really you.</font>

411
00:35:24,580 --> 00:35:26,123
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You look different.</font>

412
00:35:26,749 --> 00:35:29,418
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Papa's got a brand new 'stache.</font>

413
00:35:32,546 --> 00:35:36,174
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I knew it. I knew it!
I knew you'd come back, sir.</font>

414
00:35:36,258 --> 00:35:38,677
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I never stopped steaming
your Austrian goat's milk.</font>

415
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:45,934
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Could use some mushroom.</font>

416
00:35:47,811 --> 00:35:48,978
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You brought something.</font>

417
00:35:49,730 --> 00:35:52,524
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Some kind of space porcupine.</font>

418
00:35:53,025 --> 00:35:56,028
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Porcupine? I am an Echidna!</font>

419
00:35:56,111 --> 00:35:58,696
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Trained since birth
in all forms of lethal combat,</font>

420
00:35:58,781 --> 00:36:00,991
<font face="Comic Sans MS">destined to restore honor to my tribe,</font>

421
00:36:01,075 --> 00:36:04,870
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and willing to destroy
anything that gets in my way.</font>

422
00:36:05,496 --> 00:36:06,872
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Welcome to the team.</font>

423
00:36:13,087 --> 00:36:15,005
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That means he trusts you, Stone.</font>

424
00:36:15,631 --> 00:36:18,342
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now let's renovate this dump!</font>

425
00:36:19,009 --> 00:36:21,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Latte with steamed Austrian goat milk!</font>

426
00:36:41,657 --> 00:36:42,908
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Good one. Solid.</font>

427
00:36:50,124 --> 00:36:51,458
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Sorry, fellas.
- That's game!</font>

428
00:36:52,584 --> 00:36:54,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's how we do!</font>

429
00:36:54,795 --> 00:36:57,172
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- But are they good at math?
- Teamwork makes the dream work!</font>

430
00:36:57,798 --> 00:36:59,132
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sorry about that, Big Tom.</font>

431
00:36:59,758 --> 00:37:01,801
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Are you good?
- All good. Fine.</font>

432
00:37:01,885 --> 00:37:04,929
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Thanks for inviting me out to hang
with you and your groomsmen.</font>

433
00:37:05,013 --> 00:37:06,514
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Good quality bonding.</font>

434
00:37:07,141 --> 00:37:08,308
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You know, bro,</font>

435
00:37:08,392 --> 00:37:10,894
<font face="Comic Sans MS">those guys right there,
they're way more than my groomsmen.</font>

436
00:37:10,978 --> 00:37:12,104
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's my squad.</font>

437
00:37:12,187 --> 00:37:14,230
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Never would've made it through life
without 'em.</font>

438
00:37:14,314 --> 00:37:15,356
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Get over here!</font>

439
00:37:15,441 --> 00:37:17,151
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, I'm coming!</font>

440
00:37:17,735 --> 00:37:20,446
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- I'll catch you later.
- Hey. Yeah!</font>

441
00:37:20,529 --> 00:37:22,822
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Let me know if you're ready
for some power yoga.</font>

442
00:37:22,906 --> 00:37:25,950
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- You bet.
- Come on, Tommy boy. Let's go.</font>

443
00:37:26,034 --> 00:37:27,076
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't make me.</font>

444
00:37:28,162 --> 00:37:29,246
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What am I doing?</font>

445
00:37:29,329 --> 00:37:30,621
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, Uncle Tommy!</font>

446
00:37:30,706 --> 00:37:32,207
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, girls!</font>

447
00:37:32,291 --> 00:37:35,127
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- How you do-- Are those the wedding rings?
- Uh-huh.</font>

448
00:37:35,711 --> 00:37:36,712
<font face="Comic Sans MS">May I?</font>

449
00:37:36,795 --> 00:37:40,256
<font face="Comic Sans MS">This little ring bearer
has been taking her job very seriously.</font>

450
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:42,675
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- She's been practicing all morning.
- I can see that.</font>

451
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:45,137
<font face="Comic Sans MS">How very responsible of you.</font>

452
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:46,888
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Except aren't there supposed
to be two wedding rings?</font>

453
00:37:47,514 --> 00:37:48,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Uh-oh.</font>

454
00:37:49,892 --> 00:37:53,312
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Uncle Tommy?
- Hang on. What's going on here?</font>

455
00:37:55,731 --> 00:37:56,940
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You're gonna do great, kiddo.</font>

456
00:37:57,024 --> 00:37:58,066
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Bye.</font>

457
00:37:58,150 --> 00:37:59,526
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Hey, baby</font>

458
00:38:02,654 --> 00:38:04,656
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's right! Groom in the building!</font>

459
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:06,199
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Look at those guys.</font>

460
00:38:06,784 --> 00:38:08,202
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I wish Sonic had that.</font>

461
00:38:08,744 --> 00:38:10,954
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Muscles?
- Control yourself.</font>

462
00:38:12,039 --> 00:38:15,667
<font face="Comic Sans MS">No. Buddies. Wingmen. A squad.</font>

463
00:38:15,751 --> 00:38:19,254
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sonic doesn't have anything like that.
He's flying solo.</font>

464
00:38:20,130 --> 00:38:22,090
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Baby, you got to relax.</font>

465
00:38:22,174 --> 00:38:24,384
<font face="Comic Sans MS">You're at the Four Seasons.</font>

466
00:38:24,468 --> 00:38:27,387
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Have a mai tai.
Spend some time with your wife.</font>

467
00:38:27,471 --> 00:38:30,557
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's what he said.
Seriously, his exact words.</font>

468
00:38:30,641 --> 00:38:34,686
<font face="Comic Sans MS">See? He's a smart kid. He'll find his way.</font>

469
00:38:35,270 --> 00:38:38,356
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I absolutely cannot find my way.</font>

470
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:41,776
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We are completely, totally,
unequivocally lost.</font>

471
00:38:43,237 --> 00:38:44,696
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sonic, in this weather,</font>

472
00:38:44,780 --> 00:38:47,783
<font face="Comic Sans MS">there's no way we're gonna get
any readings on this thing!</font>

473
00:38:47,866 --> 00:38:49,617
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Should we go back?
- No, no, no.</font>

474
00:38:49,701 --> 00:38:52,954
<font face="Comic Sans MS">There's a light up ahead.
Maybe we can take shelter in there.</font>

475
00:38:58,544 --> 00:38:59,628
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Perfect.</font>

476
00:38:59,711 --> 00:39:02,880
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Are you sure about this?
We don't know who's inside.</font>

477
00:39:02,965 --> 00:39:06,218
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't worry.
On Earth, people are very welcoming,</font>

478
00:39:06,301 --> 00:39:09,679
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and love taking complete strangers
into their homes.</font>

479
00:39:39,835 --> 00:39:40,794
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Run.</font>

480
00:39:43,422 --> 00:39:45,006
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Table for two, please!</font>

481
00:39:47,134 --> 00:39:49,344
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What would you like to order?</font>

482
00:39:49,428 --> 00:39:51,138
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Two beef stews, please.</font>

483
00:39:56,602 --> 00:39:59,771
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- Where'd you get all these cool gadgets?
- I invented 'em.</font>

484
00:39:59,855 --> 00:40:01,773
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's kinda my thing.</font>

485
00:40:01,857 --> 00:40:04,317
<font face="Comic Sans MS">In fact,
my inventions are how I discovered you.</font>

486
00:40:05,152 --> 00:40:07,487
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Remember that night at the baseball field?</font>

487
00:40:07,571 --> 00:40:11,283
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Your energy blast reached all the way
to my home planet.</font>

488
00:40:11,366 --> 00:40:15,866
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I saw you save your whole village
from that crazy mustache guy.</font>

489
00:40:16,079 --> 00:40:19,290
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wait, so you've been watching me
this whole time?</font>

490
00:40:19,374 --> 00:40:20,958
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Even in the shower?</font>

491
00:40:21,043 --> 00:40:22,961
<font face="Comic Sans MS">That's a trick question.</font>

492
00:40:23,045 --> 00:40:25,255
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sonic the Hedgehog prefers bubble baths.</font>

493
00:40:25,339 --> 00:40:26,673
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Man, you're good!</font>

494
00:40:26,757 --> 00:40:29,217
<font face="Comic Sans MS">When I learned Knuckles was on your trail,</font>

495
00:40:29,301 --> 00:40:32,137
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I knew I couldn't just sit back
and watch anymore.</font>

496
00:40:32,220 --> 00:40:33,679
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I had to come warn you.</font>

497
00:40:34,932 --> 00:40:36,600
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What? Hang on one sec.</font>

498
00:40:36,683 --> 00:40:38,267
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Donut Lord is checking in.</font>

499
00:40:40,354 --> 00:40:43,899
<font face="Comic Sans MS">"Just chilling. Watching TV."</font>

500
00:40:44,399 --> 00:40:46,150
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Dot, dot, dot.</font>

501
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:48,987
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Dot, dot, dot.</font>

502
00:40:49,738 --> 00:40:51,448
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Dot, dot, dot.</font>

503
00:40:51,531 --> 00:40:53,324
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Dot, dot, dot.</font>

504
00:40:53,909 --> 00:40:56,494
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Dot, dot, dot.</font>

505
00:40:56,995 --> 00:40:57,996
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Doctor,</font>

506
00:40:58,997 --> 00:41:01,332
<font face="Comic Sans MS">why are we working with this imbecile?</font>

507
00:41:02,668 --> 00:41:07,168
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Because that simpleminded space trash
is the key to something extraordinary.</font>

508
00:41:08,173 --> 00:41:10,717
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Something to help you get revenge
on the hedgehog.</font>

509
00:41:11,218 --> 00:41:12,427
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Think bigger, Stone.</font>

510
00:41:13,011 --> 00:41:16,305
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The emerald he seeks
could power my wildest designs.</font>

511
00:41:16,390 --> 00:41:18,767
<font face="Comic Sans MS">My genius wouldn't just be recognized
on Earth.</font>

512
00:41:18,850 --> 00:41:21,853
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It would spread virally
to every corner of the galaxy,</font>

513
00:41:21,937 --> 00:41:25,190
<font face="Comic Sans MS">allowing me to harness
all the negative forces of the universe</font>

514
00:41:25,983 --> 00:41:28,235
<font face="Comic Sans MS">and commune with Darkness itself.</font>

515
00:41:28,318 --> 00:41:30,695
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wow. That sounds big.</font>

516
00:41:31,363 --> 00:41:34,532
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's been on my vision board for years.
It's the Law of Attraction.</font>

517
00:41:34,616 --> 00:41:35,950
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Didn't you see The Secret?</font>

518
00:41:37,285 --> 00:41:39,328
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Kaplooey!</font>

519
00:41:39,413 --> 00:41:40,455
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Kaplooey.</font>

520
00:41:40,539 --> 00:41:43,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS">"Another boring night at home."</font>

521
00:41:43,834 --> 00:41:45,836
<font face="Comic Sans MS">The hedgehog has returned home!</font>

522
00:41:45,919 --> 00:41:49,380
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Falsa. Which is Latin for "wrong-o."</font>

523
00:41:50,090 --> 00:41:54,302
<font face="Comic Sans MS">According to my worldwide network
cell tower triangulation, he's lying,</font>

524
00:41:55,012 --> 00:41:56,179
<font face="Comic Sans MS">all the way</font>

525
00:41:57,180 --> 00:42:01,142
<font face="Comic Sans MS">from the majestic hinterlands
of Eastern Siberia.</font>

526
00:42:01,935 --> 00:42:05,146
<font face="Comic Sans MS">He's a long-distance liar!</font>

527
00:42:09,776 --> 00:42:11,861
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Yeah, there's more where that came from.</font>

528
00:42:14,364 --> 00:42:16,449
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Tiny magic hedgehog destroyed.</font>

529
00:42:17,826 --> 00:42:19,869
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Now let's begin our quest.</font>

530
00:42:22,748 --> 00:42:23,915
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Wait.</font>

531
00:42:23,999 --> 00:42:26,459
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What about your minion? The goat milker.</font>

532
00:42:27,085 --> 00:42:29,420
<font face="Comic Sans MS">There's no room on the ship for Stone.</font>

533
00:42:29,504 --> 00:42:32,298
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I say we ditch him,
ghost him, blow him off.</font>

534
00:42:32,382 --> 00:42:33,341
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Dishonor!</font>

535
00:42:34,760 --> 00:42:37,345
<font face="Comic Sans MS">"Dis" is how I roll.</font>

536
00:42:45,395 --> 00:42:48,439
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sorry, but I asked for the beef stew.</font>

537
00:42:49,983 --> 00:42:52,235
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Your breath smells like goat poop.</font>

538
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:54,738
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What did you say?</font>

539
00:42:58,492 --> 00:42:59,910
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What's going on?</font>

540
00:43:00,911 --> 00:43:03,079
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Maybe they think it's my birthday?</font>

541
00:43:04,289 --> 00:43:07,834
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Don't worry, I'll take care of this.
Okay, everybody, take it easy.</font>

542
00:43:07,918 --> 00:43:09,961
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I'm sure there's
a perfectly good explanation</font>

543
00:43:10,045 --> 00:43:12,464
<font face="Comic Sans MS">for whatever my friend said or did.</font>

544
00:43:13,507 --> 00:43:14,257
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Stand back.</font>

545
00:43:14,382 --> 00:43:15,883
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I just farted.</font>

546
00:43:21,223 --> 00:43:22,182
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Meow?</font>

547
00:43:22,599 --> 00:43:24,601
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Throw these monsters in the fire!</font>

548
00:43:28,438 --> 00:43:31,566
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, no, no. Come on, guys.
Take it easy. Let's talk this through.</font>

549
00:43:32,150 --> 00:43:33,317
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Let's talk this through!</font>

550
00:43:34,486 --> 00:43:37,238
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Come on, come on.
Scanning Siberian customs.</font>

551
00:43:37,322 --> 00:43:41,075
<font face="Comic Sans MS">- There's got to be something in here.
- Tails, whatever you're doing, do it fast.</font>

552
00:43:41,159 --> 00:43:42,201
<font face="Comic Sans MS">I think I got it!</font>

553
00:43:42,285 --> 00:43:44,495
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Pivonka! Pivonkal</font>

554
00:43:44,579 --> 00:43:46,706
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Pivonka!</font>

555
00:44:14,359 --> 00:44:15,360
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Da.</font>

556
00:44:15,902 --> 00:44:17,028
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Pivonka!</font>

557
00:44:18,738 --> 00:44:20,948
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Tails, what's a "pivonkad'?</font>

558
00:44:21,032 --> 00:44:23,826
<font face="Comic Sans MS">It's a Siberian custom
to resolve disputes.</font>

559
00:44:23,910 --> 00:44:26,579
<font face="Comic Sans MS">If we win, they let us go. If we lose...</font>

560
00:44:32,085 --> 00:44:35,421
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay, we have to grab the map
and get out of here. Where's the map?</font>

561
00:44:35,505 --> 00:44:38,174
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, no. I left it on the table! Look!</font>

562
00:44:46,016 --> 00:44:47,142
<font face="Comic Sans MS">What?</font>

563
00:45:10,290 --> 00:45:13,001
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Oh, my God, it's a dance fight.</font>

564
00:45:14,419 --> 00:45:16,629
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Sonic, what do we do?</font>

565
00:45:16,713 --> 00:45:19,006
<font face="Comic Sans MS">We dance and get that map.</font>

566
00:45:20,800 --> 00:45:21,967
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Here we go.</font>

567
00:45:24,638 --> 00:45:26,640
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay, now let's do-- No, we're gonna go--</font>

568
00:45:33,980 --> 00:45:34,981
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay.</font>

569
00:45:43,949 --> 00:45:47,994
<font face="Comic Sans MS">Okay, this is not going well.
Channing Tatum makes it look so easy.</font>

570
00:45:48,078 --> 00:45:49,621
